# Copy to ".env.mcp" for local-only values (see docs/MCP_TOOLCHAIN_VALIDATION.md).
# ".env.mcp" is gitignored - do not commit it.
#
# Optional: used if you add a GitHub MCP server in *user-level* Cursor MCP settings
# and want to pass the token via your shell environment before starting Cursor:
# GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN=
#
# Optional: other provider tokens for *user-level* MCP servers (not committed here)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
